strategies.title: Increasing Prosperity With Positive Thinking
strategies.content: Knowing yourself is the first, and a very critical step in the process of planning your future. How can you figure out what you want to do with your life if you don’t know: What am I going to do with the  rest of my life? What is my dream job? What do I enjoy doing? What’s my passion? What kind of career fits my personality?
